    wisdom:['Renewed strength covers both dramatic seasons and ordinary weary days','Long grief needs sustained hope, not just an initial burst of faith','Walking without fainting is as much a promise as soaring'],
    questions:['In this season of long grief, what would it look like to ask God specifically for strength to simply walk today, rather than soar?'],
