    questions:['What would help you actually rest this week — and could you treat pursuing that rest as an act of trust in God rather than avoidance of grief?'],
    prayer:'Lord, You alone make me dwell in safety. Help me lie down and actually sleep, trusting You with what I cannot resolve tonight. Amen.',
